<!-- QUICK SUMMARY -->
<section class="card pad">
<h2>What is a Star Citizen Free Fly event?</h2>
<p>
A Free Fly event is an official limited-time period where anyone can play Star Citizen without purchasing a game package.  
Players create an RSI account, download the launcher, and receive temporary access to selected ships and locations.
</p>

<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>Feature</th>
<th>Free Fly Access</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>Game Purchase Required</td>
<td>No</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Access Duration</td>
<td>Limited event period</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Ships Available</td>
<td>Curated rotating selection</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Progress Saved</td>
<td>Account progress persists</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Referral Bonus Eligible</td>
<td>Yes (during account creation)</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>

</section>

<!-- HOW TO JOIN -->
<section class="card pad">
<h2>How to join Star Citizen Free Fly (Step-by-Step)</h2>

<ol>
<li>Create a new RSI account during an active Free Fly.</li>
<li>Enter a referral code before finishing registration (cannot be added later).</li>
<li>Download and install the RSI Launcher.</li>
<li>Install the current game build.</li>
<li>Launch the game and choose a starting location.</li>
</ol>

<h3>Why entering a referral code matters</h3>
<p>
Free Fly is the ideal moment to activate a referral code because it must be entered at account creation.  
It does not increase the price of the game and simply activates the available new-player bonus.
</p>

</section>

