<td>Invictus Launch Week</td>
<td>May</td>
<td>Military ship focus</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Intergalactic Aerospace Expo (IAE)</td>
<td>November</td>
<td>Largest ship variety</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Patch Milestones</td>
