<!-- IS IT WORTH IT -->
<section class="card pad">
<h2>Is Star Citizen Free Fly worth trying?</h2>

<h3>Advantages</h3>
<ul>
<li>No financial commitment</li>
<li>Test performance on your hardware</li>
<li>Access multiple ship roles</li>
<li>Evaluate gameplay loops before buying</li>
</ul>

<h3>Considerations</h3>
<ul>
<li>Server load may be higher during events</li>
<li>Performance varies by system</li>
<li>Access ends when the event ends</li>
</ul>

<p>
Free Fly is ideal for players who want a realistic preview before purchasing a starter package.
</p>

</section>

<!-- FAQ -->
<section class="card pad">
<h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

<details>
<summary>Do I need to buy the game during Free Fly?</summary>
<p>No. Access is granted temporarily without purchase.</p>
</details>

<details>
<summary>Can I keep my progress after Free Fly?</summary>
<p>Your account persists. Continued play requires purchasing a starter package.</p>
</details>

<details>
<summary>Can I add a referral code later?</summary>
<p>No. Referral codes must be entered during account creation.</p>
</details>

<details>
<summary>How long do Free Fly events last?</summary>
<p>Typically between 5–10 days depending on the event.</p>
</details>

</section>

